Verify all scripts are in the same directory
Check Python path: export PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:$(pwd)
Conclusion
This lab demonstrated AI-specific security threats through hands-on simulation of prompt leakage attacks. You created a vulnerable AI application, exploited it using various prompt injection techniques, and built detection and alerting systems to identify such attacks. These skills are essential for securing AI systems in production environments.

Key takeaways:

AI systems require specialized security measures beyond traditional approaches
Prompt injection is a critical vulnerability in LLM-based applications
Log analysis and pattern matching can detect AI-specific attacks
Automated alerting enables rapid response to security incidents
Defense-in-depth strategies are essential for AI security
